<br>
They say that the higher your intelligence the faster you learn skills... or your skill levels go up quicker.  I've noticed however that your skill increases even when you fail on an attempt... so I'd wager that the only way you can get less failures is to follow the trivials charts on those websites.  When you've reached the trivial level for a certain gem/metal combination you will very rarely fail, but your skills will also stop increasing while you work with that combination. <p>Dellenn<BR>
