<br>
If you are doing this skill simply to make money, get ready for a dissapointment. Your initial investment, and fails will more than outgrow your successes and sales. If you're getting into this to aid your guild/friends, then you're gonna be a happy jewelcrafter. Thats what I use it for, and even with a 198 skill, my success rates are usually high enough that it costs me less to make plat/velium items for my fiends than it does to buy em on the open market. <p>Slymie Ras <br>
