<br>
INT affects your skill raises (just like in many other trade skills.)<br>
<br>
WIS affects your success rate with a minor secondary check on a failure.<br>
<br>
To correct a couple fallacies here:<br>
<br>
Specialization is not available till lvl 20, not 16.<br>
<br>
You don't get a price difference of any note until Gold, not Electrum.  If you spend your time enchanting those bars of Electrum you will be at it a HORRIBLY long time.  At about Gold Emerald you start to notice a nice sell back difference.  Remember to Illusion the race of the place you are selling for a nice increase in plat.<br>
